sentence: In 1993, Grohl was recruited to help recreate the music of The Beatles ' early years for the movie Backbeat; he played drums in an all-star lineup that included Greg Dull of the Afghan Whigs, indie producer Don Fleming, Mike Mills of R.E.M., Thurston Moore of Sonic Youth, and Dave Pirner of Soul Asylum.
